e-execute-radio&amp;utm_term=scsf-594725&amp;utm_content=a0xRn000000rzgdIAA&amp;scsonar=1" target="_blank">现在可以以 149.99 美元</a>（原价 250 美元）购买 Eton Elite Executive 收音机，但价格可能随时变化。</p><div class="mx-auto mt-8 w-full max-w-4xl"><div id="video-container-De2eSbgOvMU"></div></div> ]]>;</content:encoded><link/> https://lifehacker.com/eton-elite-executive-radio-sale<author>堆栈商务</author><category><![CDATA[Tech]]></category></item><item><title>最适合小衣柜的机库</title><guid ispermalink="false">01HVVSYGJ3W6GYRESW0NP92Q44</guid><pubDate> Fri, 19 Apr 2024 23:00:00 +0000</pubDate><description>层叠衣架对于整理小壁橱非常有帮助，但每种衣架都有优点和缺点。 </description><media:thumbnail url="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HVVSYGJ3W6GYRESW0NP92Q44/hero-image.png"></media:thumbnail><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>我写了很多关于<a href="https://lifehacker.com/home/use-the-12-12-12-decluttering-method" target="_blank">整理</a>和<a href="https://lifehacker.com/home/best-storage-solutions-for-bags-and-purses" target="_blank">整理的</a>文章，尤其是在壁橱方面，那是因为我一直处于彻底检修自己壁橱的状态。可以容纳多件衣服的分层层叠衣架是小壁橱的首选解决方案，但有几种不同的衣架可以做不同的事情。在您购买您看到的第一套之前，让我帮助您找出最适合您需求的类型。</p><h2>不同类型的层叠吊架</h2><p>您可以获得几种不同类型的层叠衣架。目前，我有两种：一种是悬挂式金属链条品种，另一种是更坚硬的塑料链条品种。 </p><div class="eloquent-imagery-image"><div class="flex justify-center"><img class="border border-gray-100" src="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HVVSYGJ3W6GYRESW0NP92Q44/images-1.fill.size_2000x1125.v1713551393.png" alt="两种并排的层叠吊架" width="2000" height="1125" loading="lazy" srcset="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HVVSYGJ3W6GYRESW0NP92Q44/images-1.fill.size_800x450.v1713551393.png 800w, https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HVVSYGJ3W6GYRESW0NP92Q44/images-1.fill.size_1400x788.v1713551393.png 1400w, https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HVVSYGJ3W6GYRESW0NP92Q44/images-1.fill.size_2000x1125.v1713551393.png 2000w" sizes="(max-width: 1408px) 100vw, 1408px"></div><div class="mt-2"><span class="mt-2 font-akshar text-sm tracking-wide">左边是金属层叠衣架，右边是塑料衣架。</span><span class="text-xs inline-block text-gray-600">图片来源：林赛·埃勒夫森</span></div></div><p>过去，我主要使用塑料类型，但它们的第一个主要缺点是，它们可能会因承受太大的重量而破裂，或者重量会慢慢拉低悬挂在杆周围的部分，使其变形并最终使其变得毫无用处。由于这些原因，我已经使用过很多塑料的，这就是为什么我几个月前订购了金属的。</p><p>然而，金属也有其自身的挑战。虽然它们更坚固，可以承受更多的重量，并且不会变形，但当您试图在杆上移动链条时，链条的流畅运动非常烦人。我在悬挂的衣服后面放了一个搁架单元（这本身就是一个衣柜整理技巧），所以我必须始终移动悬挂部件才能访问架子上折叠的物品。从顶部抓住链条吊架并沿着杆拖动它几乎总是会导致两个或三个吊架从链条上的插槽中掉落，而对于更坚硬的塑料版本则不会发生这种情况。</p><h2>选择层叠衣架</h2><p>如果您的衣服很轻或者需要经常移动衣架，请选择刚性的衣服，如下所示：</p><ul><li><p> <a href="https://zdcs.link/x3DWk?pageview_type=Standard&amp;template=Roundups&amp;module=content-body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=eight%20pack%20of%20plastic%20space-saving%20hangers%20from%20Gillraj&amp;short_url=x3DWk&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="nofollow sponsored" target="_blank" title="（在新窗口中打开）">Gillraj 的八件装节省空间的塑料衣架</a>。 （8.99 美元）</p></li><li><p> <a href="https://zdcs.link/5qPo8?pageview_type=Standard&amp;template=Roundups&amp;module=content-body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=100%20standalone%20hooks%20that%20attach%20to%20regular%20hangers&amp;short_url=5qPo8&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="nofollow sponsored" target="_blank" title="（在新窗口中打开）">100 个独立挂钩，可连接到常规衣架上</a>，因此您可以根据需要制作衣服链。 （9.99 美元）</p></li></ul><p>如果您的衣服较重，请考虑金属版本以获得最大的支撑力：</p><ul><li><p> <a href="https://zdcs.link/R2B41?pageview_type=Standard&amp;template=Roundups&amp;module=content-body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=six%20pack%20of%20hanging%20chains&amp;short_url=R2B41&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="nofollow sponsored" target="_blank" title="（在新窗口中打开）">六块装的吊链</a>。 ($6.99)</p></li></ul><p>如果您想要两全其美 - 一个坚固、不变形<em>且</em>坚固的层叠衣架 - 使用这款开槽金属衣架即可实现差异化：</p><div class="mb-4 rounded-md border-2 border-gray-100 py-4 shadow-lg"> <a href="https://cc.lifehacker.com/v1/otc/06ZVRiLmglGs4QA6plTXzTC?url=https%3A%2F%2Fzdcs.link%2FNxNmX&amp;template=Roundups&amp;module=shop-card&amp;element=offer&amp;item=whole-shop-card&amp;position=&amp;element_label=Magic+Clothing+Hangers+Space+Saving+Sturdy+Metal+Hangers+Wardrobe+Closet+Organizer+Space+Saving+Hanger+%28Pack+of+12%29+&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss&amp;short_code=https%3A%2F%2Fzdcs.link%2FNxNmX" data-commerce="1" target="_blank" rel="nofollow sponsored" data-parent-group="affiliate-link" title="（在新窗口中打开）" class="cursor-default no-underline" data-ga-click="data-ga-click" data-ga-item="whole-shop-card" data-ga-label="Magic Clothing Hangers Space Saving Sturdy Metal Hangers Wardrobe Closet Organizer Space Saving Hanger (Pack of 12)"><div class="my-2 ml-4 font-akshar text-2xl font-medium leading-7 text-brand-green md:text-left">
            </div></a><div class="flex flex-wrap justify-between px-6 text-black no-underline md:flex-nowrap md:px-4"><div class="order-1 mx-auto md:order-2 md:ml-4 md:flex md:w-full md:grow md:flex-col"><div class="block text-center font-akshar text-2xl font-medium leading-7 text-brand-green md:text-left">魔术衣架节省空间坚固金属衣架衣柜壁橱整理器节省空间衣架（12 件装）</div><div class="mt-2 block font-sans text-sm font-medium leading-5 text-gray-900 md:mx-0 md:mt-2">金属层叠衣架</div><div class="mt-2 hidden md:flex md:grow md:justify-between"><div class="self-end"><div class="mb-0 h-11 md:flex md:flex-col md:justify-center"><div class=" font-sans leading-3 text-black"><div class="text-center md:text-left"><span class="text-sm font-medium md:text-xs">亚马逊</span><span class="text-base font-bold md:text-sm">29.99 美元</span><img class="mx-auto mt-0 inline" src="/images/amazon-prime.svg" title="亚马逊 Prime" alt="Amazon Prime" width="42" height="15"></div><div class="my-0 text-center md:text-left"> <span class="text-sm font-bold line-through md:text-xs">$35.99</span><span class="text-base font-bold text-brand-green md:text-sm">节省 $6.00</span> </div></div></div></div><div class="w-44 self-end"><div class="h-11 hover:cursor-pointer"><div class="w-full rounded-md bg-brand-green py-3 text-center font-sans text-sm text-white"><span>现在去购物</span></div></div></div></div></div><div class="order-2 mt-5 w-full md:order-1 md:mt-0 md:hidden"><img class="m-auto w-full rounded-md rounded-md border border-2 border-brand-green-100" src="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HVVSYGJ3W6GYRESW0NP92Q44/images-2.fill.size_245x225.v1713551393.png" alt="层叠吊架" width="245" height="225" loading="lazy"></div><div class="order-2 mt-2 hidden w-64 md:order-1 md:mt-0 md:block"><img class="m-auto w-full rounded-md border border-2 border-brand-green-100" src="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HVVSYGJ3W6GYRESW0NP92Q44/images-2.fill.size_245x225.v1713551393.png" alt="层叠吊架" width="245" height="225" loading="lazy"></div><div class="order-3 flex grow flex-wrap md:hidden md:grow-0"><div class="mt-5 w-full"><div class=" hover:cursor-pointer"><div class="w-full rounded-md bg-brand-green py-3 text-center font-sans text-sm text-white"><span>现在去购物</span></div></div></div><div class="mx-2 mt-2 w-full"><div class=" font-sans leading-3 text-black"><div class="text-center md:text-left"><span class="text-sm font-medium md:text-xs">亚马逊</span><span class="text-base font-bold md:text-sm">29.99 美元</span><img class="mx-auto mt-0 inline" src="/images/amazon-prime.svg" title="亚马逊 Prime" alt="Amazon Prime" width="42" height="15"></div><div class="my-0 text-center md:text-left"> <span class="text-sm font-bold line-through md:text-xs">$35.99</span><span class="text-base font-bold text-brand-green md:text-sm">节省 $6.00</span></div></div></div></div></div></div><p>除此之外，您还可以使用<a href="https://zdcs.link/ln60O?pageview_type=Standard&amp;template=Roundups&amp;module=content-body&amp;element=offer&amp;item=text-link&amp;element_label=over-the-door%20racks&amp;short_url=ln60O&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Flifehacker.com%2Ffeed%2Frss" rel="nofollow sponsored" target="_blank" title="（在新窗口中打开）">门上的架子</a>来存放较重的物品，例如外套、西装外套和连衣裙。它们相对便宜，并且让您在打开门时更容易看到所有物品。如果你假装得足够努力，那几乎就像拥有一个步入式衣柜一样。</p> ]]>;</content:encoded><link/> https://lifehacker.com/home/best-hangers-for-a-small-closet<author>林赛·埃勒夫森</author><category><![CDATA[Cleaning & Organizing]]></category></item><item><title>按门铃和摄像头现可享受高达 44% 的折扣</title><guid ispermalink="false">01HVW1K8XV7GNNFWCWFBM9XBPF</guid><pubDate> Fri, 19 Apr 2024 22:30:10 +0000</pubDate><description>门铃、室内和室外摄像头以及大量泛光灯。 </description><media:thumbnail url="https://lifehacker.com/imagery/articles/01HVW1K8XV7GNNFWCWFBM9XBPF/hero-image.png"></media:thumbnail><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>亚马逊同时拥有 Blink 和 Ring，虽然<a href="https://lifehacker.com/tech/ring-and-blink-doorbell-comparison" target="_blank">它们之间存在重大差异</a>，但您可以简单地将 Ring 视为更高端的产品。如果您确信<a href="https://lifehacker.com/tech/how-to-install-ring-doorbell" target="_blank">Ring 产品